{"tid":1898767,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"AirTag 定位裝置細節曝光，將採用磁吸式充電","createTime":"2020-02-26T08:32:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T12:35:04.000Z","uid":298405,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4297106ed6faee481965f121222497ce8d85f9fd","tid":1898767,"uid":298405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T08:32:34.000Z","msg":"日前有傳聞指蘋果將會在 3 月底舉行春季發表會，正式發表 AirTag 追蹤配件，這個早在去年就在網路流傳的裝置，最近有更多細節流出。根據日本網站 Mac Otakara 報導，AirTag 將完全防水，同時採用類似蘋果 Watch 的磁吸式充電技術。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/25104456/apple-AirTag-624x349.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F25104456%2Fapple-AirTag-624x349.jpg&h=402249fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去年夏天發表的 iOS 13，人們在程式碼找到 AirTag 一些蛛絲馬跡，這塊和 Tile 功能類似的配件，讓 iOS 裝置用戶可用 Find My 程式定位，進而尋回失物。受惠於蘋果自家 U1 晶片，AirTag 將提供離線搜尋功能，就算裝置沒電也可以透過其他 iPhone、iPad 或 Mac 發送加密訊號，協助提供裝置的精確定位。<br />\n<br />\n雖然 AirTag 有望在 3 月底發表，但名分析師郭明錤稍早預測，AirTag 要到今年第二或第三季才有望上市；Mac Otakara 則更保守，預測 AirTag 可能會留待今年秋季發表會才公布。<br />\n<br />\n等睇變fail product<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f2c38ed8a9308ac5e91e316f6c0a54fa68f08f","tid":1898767,"uid":89514,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T08:54:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32cfa1cfec78eb9c611d571a508287fe65cb3008","tid":1898767,"uid":180814,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T08:58:22.000Z","msg":"暫時睇唔出呢舊嘢有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6665ff8c441a4ed73384b49b0d0e0f4bcf36bfbd","tid":1898767,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32cfa1cfec78eb9c611d571a508287fe65cb3008","tid":1898767,"uid":180814,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T08:58:22.000Z","msg":"暫時睇唔出呢舊嘢有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" cl